title: QA Team expansion
body:
PankakeSwap increases it's QA team to test ensure browser/dapp crossplatform functionality as to ensure revenue stream and community engagement does not get hindered by simple and small compatibility issues in regards to user interaction. 

This could potentially take form of external team to ensure unbiased testing as well as increasing security and trust with the community and potential investors.

The underlying idea is that it would pay itself back in the long run with PankakeSwap being more accessible to more users thus increasing revenue and token value.
